=== New RPCs ===
update_deal_seller_v1(p_deal_id uuid, p_fields jsonb)
  - SECURITY DEFINER, authenticated only
  - workspace write lock enforced via check_workspace_write_allowed_v1()
  - jsonb payload keys: seller_name, seller_phone, seller_email, seller_pain, seller_timeline, seller_notes
  - omit key = no change
  - explicit null = clear field
  - same value as current = VALIDATION_ERROR
  - empty or non-object payload = VALIDATION_ERROR
  - unknown keys = VALIDATION_ERROR
  - zero rows updated disambiguated: NOT_FOUND vs VALIDATION_ERROR

update_deal_property_v1(p_deal_id uuid, p_fields jsonb)
  - SECURITY DEFINER, authenticated only
  - workspace write lock enforced via check_workspace_write_allowed_v1()
  - jsonb payload keys: address, next_action, next_action_due
  - next_action_due validated as timestamptz before UPDATE
  - same field contract as update_deal_seller_v1
  - zero rows updated disambiguated: NOT_FOUND vs VALIDATION_ERROR

